{"id": "noos012", "name": "Audio_Nora_694_03_08", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "Nora, time for dinner.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "(Nods)\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Afterward, we'll draw blood for the new formula. That will be it for today. You can go to bed after the blood draw, understand?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "(Nods)\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "Director, this child... she's three years old already, yet she still can't talk?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Yes... But her cognitive abilities are working normally.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "Could it have something to do with her immunity?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "In science, the crucial thing is actual evidence. Before I can get a definitive confirmation, I will not make any hasty conclusions.\nYou, go ask A team to prepare the equipment we'll be using later.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "Yes sir... Ah, apologies. I forgot to schedule the phlebotomy room. Director, can you sign this for me? I don't want a time conflict with another team.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "... Hey, you seem pretty capable when you were in Kim's team. That's why I transferred you over here to be an assistant. Yet you screw up right away.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "I'm sorry...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Hand me the board. I won't be so kind next time. How many units did you draw last time? Do you have the notes?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "Ah... I... that... I'm really sorry! I forgot this one as well...\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "You little...\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "Eek!\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "Ah... Ah... (four fingers)\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Hmm? Ho? Is it forty...?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "Hmm. (Nods)\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Thank you, Nora.\nIt's because of Nora that you are spared a serious beating. You better thank her.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "... She... understands what we are saying?\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "As a matter of fact, Nora's intelligence has already far surpassed that of a regular child in the same age range. However, due to her inability to talk, there are a lot of things we simply can't measure.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "... Amazing.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Stop spacing out. Proceed with the preparations.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "Ah! Yes, sir!\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Is she asleep?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "Yes.\nWhen she's asleep... she looks just like a normal child. It's really hard to imagine that she is so important to the research.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Her genes are the keys to the world for us humans. The new medicine we made this time have to be effective...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "Hmm......\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "......?\nDirector, wait a second. Something's not right with Nora.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "Ugh...\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "Her eyeballs are moving around rapidly. Is she having a nightmare...?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "Yikes! She is having a nosebleed! Nora! Nora...\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Wait! Don't wake her up for now!\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "Umm......\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "It stopped... Director, why did that happen?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "I have no idea... The surveillance cameras recorded the whole process, right? Retrieve the recording and save it now.\nActually, this is already the third time this has happened. Starting next week, we'll let Nora sleep in the BIT silent chamber and see if we can discover anything from her brainwave activities.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member I"], "content": "Got it...\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "ドアが開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "Noraちゃん、ご飯だよ。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "（うなずく）\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "あとで新しい処方用に血液を採取するからね。\n今日はこれでおしまい。\n終わったら、寝ていいよ。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "（うなずく）\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "チーフ、この子……もう3歳になるのにまだ話しませんね……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "そうだな……\nだが、認識はしているみたいだ。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "免疫の体質と関係があるのでしょうか？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "科学で最も重要なのは実証だ。\n確実な証拠が手に入るまでは、何事も結論付けることはできん。\nA班にこの後使うものを用意させるんだ。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "はい……あ、申し訳ありません。\n採血室の申請を忘れていました。\nチーフ、サインをお願いしてもいいですか？\n誰かに取られてしまうと困るので……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……おいおい、私はお前が優秀だと思ってキムの所から引き抜いたのだぞ？\nさっそくミスか？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "すみません……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "ボードを貸すんだ。次はないぞ。\n前回はいくら取った？記録は？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "あ……えっと……す、すみません！\n忘れました……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "お前……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "うわぁ！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "あ……あ……（指で4を示す）\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "ん？おや？40か……？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "ん（うなずく）\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Nora、ありがとう。\nNoraのおかげで殴られずに済んだぞ。\n感謝するんだな。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "……この子は……私たちの会話が分かっているんですか？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Noraの知能レベルはすでに他の同じ年頃の子供を上回っている。\nただ、この子は話せないから、テストをするのも難しい。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "……すごいですね……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "ボーっとしてないで、早く準備を進めたらどうだね？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "あ！はい！\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "ドアが開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "寝たか？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "はい。\n寝ていると……他の子どもと同じですね。\n我々の実験において、そんなに重要な役割を果たす子供には到底見えません。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "この子のDNAは人類が世界の扉を開くための鍵だ。\n今回の新しい薬は必ず成功させなくてはならない……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "ん……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "………？\nチーフ、Noraちゃんの様子が変です。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "うっ……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "眼球が激しく動いてる。\n悪夢でも見てるんでしょうか……？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "うわ！鼻血です！\nNoraちゃん！Noraちゃ……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "待て！起こすな！\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "うっ…ぅぅ……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "止まった……チーフ、どういうことでしょう？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "私にも分からない……監視カメラに記録が残っているはずだな？\n確認しろ。\nこれがはじめてではない……3回目だ。\n来週から、寝る時はBIT静置キャビンで寝かせよう。\n脳波からなにか分かるかもしれん。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員I"], "content": "はい……\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "Nora，吃飯囉。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "（點頭）\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "晚點要做新配方用的抽血，今天只要這樣。抽完就可以睡覺了，好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "（點頭）\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "主任，這孩子……都已經三歲左右了，還不會說話嗎？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "嗯……不過認知沒有問題。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "會不會跟她免疫的體質有關？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "科學講求實證，在沒有得出確切的證據前我不妄下定論。\n你去請 A 組準備待會要用的東西吧。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "好的……啊，抱歉，我忘記申請抽血室了。主任可以幫我簽個名嗎？怕待會跟別人撞到時間。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……喂，我看你幹得不錯才把你從金那邊調過來當助手，馬上就出包了。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "對不起……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "板子拿來，下不為例。\n上次抽是多少單位？有紀錄嗎？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "啊……這我也……真的很對不起！我忘記了……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "你這……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "噫！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "啊……啊……（手指比四）\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "嗯？喔？四十嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "嗯。（點頭）\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "謝謝妳啊，Nora。\n感謝 Nora 免你挨一頓揍吧。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "……她……聽得懂我們說的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "其實 Nora 的智商反應已經遠遠超越一般同齡小孩該有的水準。不過因為她不會說話，很多東西我們很難測出來。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "……好厲害。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "別傻在這了，快去準備。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "啊！好！\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "她睡著了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "嗯。\n睡覺的樣子……就像一般的小孩一樣。實在很難想像她對研究這麼重要。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "她的基因是打開人類通往世界之門的鑰匙，這次新版的藥我們一定要成功才行……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "……？\n主任，等一下，Nora 的樣子不太對。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "唔唔……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "眼球在劇烈運動，做惡夢了嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "哇！她流鼻血了！Nora！Nora……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "等等！先別叫醒她！\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "唔唔……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "停了……主任，怎麼會這樣？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "我不知道……剛才的監視器都錄下來了吧？快點紀錄起來。\n這其實已經是第三次了，下週開始 Nora 睡覺讓她在 BIT 靜置艙睡。看看能不能從腦波運動發現什麼。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "好……\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "Nora~ 밥 먹을 시간이야~\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "(고개를 끄덕인다)\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "나중에 새로운 약의 처방을 위해서 혈액을 채취할 거, 오늘은 이것만 하면 돼. 채취가 끝나면 바로 자도 괜찮아. 알았지?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "(고개를 끄덕인다)\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "주임님, 이 아이... 벌써 3살이나 됐는데도 아직 말을 못하는 건가요?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "그래... \n그래도 인지 능력에는 아무런 문제가 발견되지 않았어.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "면역 체질과 관련이 있는 것은 아닐까요?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "과학은 언제나 실증을 추구한다. 나는 정확한 근거 없이 함부로 정의를 내리는 일은 일절 하지 않는다. 넌 A팀에게 가서 조금 이따가 사용할 것들을 준비하라고 전해라.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "알겠습니다....아, 죄송합니다. 혈액 채취실 사용 신청을 깜빡하고... 괜찮으시다면 주임님께서 결제해주실 수 있을까요? 다른 사람들과 시간이 겹칠 우려가 있어서...\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": ".....이봐, 난 네가 우수한 놈이라고 생각했다. 그래서 김이 있던 곳에서 널 빼와서 내 조수로 둔 것이지. 그런데 이렇게 바로 밑바닥을 내보이는 건가?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "죄송합니다...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "이리 내놔라. 이번 한 번만 봐주도록 하지. 다음은 없다. 저번 채취량은? 기록해 뒀나?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "아... 저 그게... 정말 죄송합니다... 깜빡하고...\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "네놈이 정말...\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "으아악!\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "아... 아...(손가락 4개를 든다)\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "응? 아... 40이란... 말이니?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "응(고개를 끄덕인다)\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "고맙구나 Nora.\n네놈은 Nora에게 감사해라. 덕분에 덜 얻어맞게 되었으니깐.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "...이 아이... 우리가 하는 말을 알아듣는 겁니까?\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "사실 Nora의 지능 지수는 이미 동연령대 아이들의 수준을 훨씬 상회하고 있다. 하지만 아직 말을 못하기 때문에, 정확하게 평가하기가 어려울 뿐이지.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "...대단하군요...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "여기서 멍청히 있지 말고 빨리 가서 준비나 해.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "앗! 네! 알겠습니다!\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "잠들었나?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "네. 이렇게 잠든 모습을 보면... 일반 어린애와 다를 게 없어 보이는데. 사실 이 아이가 연구의 열쇠라는 사실이 아직 실감이 나지 않습니다.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "이 아이의 DNA는 인류가 세계의 문을 열게 될 열쇠다. 이번 신약 개발은 무조건 성공시켜야만 해.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "으...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "...?\n주임님! 잠시만요, Nora의 상태가 심상치 않습니다!\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "우으으...\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "안구 운동이 매우 격렬히 진행되고 있습니다! 악몽이라도 꾸고 있는 건가...?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "으앗! 코피를 흘립니다! Nora! Nora......\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "잠깐! 깨우지 마라!\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "으으으...\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "멈췄다...... 주임님, 왜 이런 거죠?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "나도 자세히는 모른다. 감시 카메라에 방금 있었던 일은 모두 기록되어 있겠지? 어서 빨리 확인해 보도록.\n사실 이런 증상이 있던 것이 이번이 벌써 세 번째다. 다음 주부터   Nora는 BIT 수면 캐비닛에 재울 생각이야. 뇌파의 움직임으로부터 뭔가 발견할 수 있을지도 모른다.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 I"], "content": "알겠습니다...\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "Nora，吃飯囉。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "（點頭）\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "晚點要做新配方用的抽血，今天只要這樣。抽完就可以睡覺了，好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "（點頭）\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "主任，這孩子……都已經三歲左右了，還不會說話嗎？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "嗯……不過認知沒有問題。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "會不會跟她免疫的體質有關？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "科學講求實證，在沒有得出確切的證據前我不妄下定論。\n你去請 A 組準備待會要用的東西吧。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "好的……啊，抱歉，我忘記申請抽血室了。主任可以幫我簽個名嗎？怕待會跟別人撞到時間。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……喂，我看你幹得不錯才把你從金那邊調過來當助手，馬上就出包了。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "對不起……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "板子拿來，下不為例。\n上次抽是多少單位？有紀錄嗎？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "啊……這我也……真的很對不起！我忘記了……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "你這……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "噫！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "啊……啊……（手指比四）\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "嗯？喔？四十嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "嗯。（點頭）\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "謝謝妳啊，Nora。\n感謝 Nora 免你挨一頓揍吧。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 I"], "content": "……她……聽得懂我們說的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 22